Light on Conspiracies - Side Thorn and Conspiracy Granny Interview (2017)

Light-On-Conspiracies-Side-Thorn-Conspiracy-Granny-Part-1.mp3 - 54min 55s 34.6 kb/s
Light-On-Conspiracies-Side-Thorn-and-Conspiracy-Granny-Part-2.mp3 - 

Ole Dammegard interviews Side Thorn and Conspiracy Granny, an ‘ordinary’ pair of Texans who have just had enough of all the false flag operations put in motion to force the population into obedience.

They have taken on the task of exposing as many of them as possible, by going on location with hidden cameras.

In addition, Side Thorn has put up a reward of USD 100.000 to anyone who can prove real deaths at Sandy Hook and in many more of these alleged ‘terror attacks.
